title: [Surf] New Emissions of Light and Sound (Globe) DVDrip
description: Another ground-breaking film made by the people who brought you SECRET MACHINE. This time, we've partnered up with world-renowned electronica DJ SASHA to create an audio-visual experience like nothing the surf world has ever seen. Watch TAJ BURROW, CJ HOBGOOD, DAMIEN HOBGOOD, YADIN NICOL, and NATHAN WEBSTER slide by as you get lost in this trip. Sit back, relax, and open your mind. It's going to be a nice ride.
